---
layout: layouts/base.liquid
title: Homepage - My Eleventy Site
metaDescription: Welcome to the homepage of my awesome Eleventy site with Tailwind CSS and Vite.
---
<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-6">{{ title }}</h1>
  <p class="mb-4 text-lg">Welcome to the Eleventy starter project, now with Vite integration!</p>

  <section class="my-8 p-6 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg shadow-md">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-4">About This Setup</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">
      This project demonstrates a manual integration of Vite with Eleventy for optimized asset bundling (CSS and JavaScript).
      Tailwind CSS is processed by Vite, and Jest/Playwright are configured for testing.
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-600">
      Check out the <code class="bg-gray-200 px-1 rounded">src/_data/vite.js</code> file and the updated <code class="bg-gray-200 px-1 rounded">src/_includes/layouts/base.liquid</code>
      to see how assets are handled in development and production.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="my-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-4">Latest Blog Posts</h2>
    {% if collections.posts.length > 0 %}
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        {% for post in collections.posts limit: 3 %}
          <li class="p-4 border border-gray-300 rounded-md hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-blue-700 hover:text-blue-800">
              <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-1">
              Published on: <time datetime="{{ post.date | date: '%Y-%m-%d' }}">{{ post.date | date: "%B %-d, %Y" }}</time>
            </p>
            {% if post.data.tags and post.data.tags.length > 0 %}
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">
                Tags: 
                {% for tag in post.data.tags %}
                  <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">{{ tag }}</span>
                {% endfor %}
              </p>
            {% endif %}
          </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
      {% if collections.posts.length > 3 %}
        <p class="mt-4"><a href="/posts/" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">View all posts...</a></p>
      {% endif %}
    {% else %}
      <p class="text-gray-600">No blog posts yet. Stay tuned!</p>
    {% endif %}
  </section>

  <section class="my-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
    {% include "components/form-contact.liquid" %}
  </section>

</div>
